OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780330269
OL,3,CFive new llamas join research herd at
OL,4,CReading farm used to help treat viruses
OL,6,FProfessor Gary Stephens, who leads the
OL,7,Fnanobody service at the University of
OL,8,FReading, said: "It is always a
OL,9,Fbrilliant day when new llamas arrive
OL,10,Fon the farm.
OL,12,F"We love these animals and we get very
OL,13,Fattached to them, they all have great
OL,14,Fpersonalities.
OL,16,F"Their welfare is absolutely our
OL,17,Fpriority and we take enormous pride in
OL,18,Flooking after them to the very highest
OL,19,Fstandards.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780330269
OL,3,CFive new llamas join research herd at
OL,4,CReading farm used to help treat viruses
OL,6,F"But they are also doing something
OL,7,Fquite incredible.
OL,9,F"The nanobodies we get from them are
OL,10,Fbeing used in research that could one
OL,11,Fday change how we treat cancer,
OL,12,Finfectious diseases and much more.
OL,14,F"They are rather extraordinary
OL,15,Fcreatures."
OL,17,FThe llamas are central to research
OL,18,Finto nanobodies, a type of miniature
OL,19,Fantibody that only certain animals,
OL,20,Fincluding llamas, can produce.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
