PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780330269
OL,3,CFive new llamas join research herd at
OL,4,CReading farm used to help treat viruses
OL,6,FNanobodies are far smaller than
OL,7,Fstandard human antibodies, making them
OL,8,Feasier to engineer into drugs and use
OL,9,Fas new research tools.
OL,11,FScientists extract nanobodies from the
OL,12,Fllamas' blood after exposing the
OL,13,Fanimals to a small quantity of a virus
OL,14,For protein, a process similar to
OL,15,Fvaccination. The llamas are not harmed.
OL,17,FDuring the Covid-19 pandemic,
OL,18,Fnanobodies from the Reading herd
OL,19,Fcontributed to research into
OL,20,Ftreatments for the virus.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
