OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780330269
OL,3,CFive new llamas join research herd at
OL,4,CReading farm used to help treat viruses
OL,6,FDr Anna Selezneva, Business
OL,7,FDevelopment Officer for Nanobody
OL,8,FTechnical Service, said: "Llamatech
OL,9,FNBS is proud to be building on the
OL,10,FUniversity of Reading's long-standing
OL,11,Fexpertise in nanobody research and
OL,12,Fcamelid care.
OL,14,F"Our aim is to make this unique
OL,15,Fcapability more accessible to
OL,16,Fresearchers and industry partners,
OL,17,Fboth in the UK and internationally,
OL,18,Fwhile maintaining the highest
OL,19,Fstandards of animal welfare, ethics
OL,20,Fand scientific quality.
